{"tid":1768925,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"茂名唔做林奠2.0 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-04T12:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:48:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e7a116cbd7b3b4c54de8d9637307abdaae42cf","tid":1768925,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191204/20818270/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191204%2F20818270%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDZFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=3589786f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191204%2F20818270%2F&h=f50ee7a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191204/20818270/</a><br />\n<br />\n茂名唔做林奠2.0 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191204/large/1575356135_f16c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575356135_f16c.jpg&h=ab01305c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東茂名化州黨幹同志，學晒特衰政府，哄騙居民同意興建「人文生態園」。但騙局火速爆煲，生態園原來是火葬場。民眾驚覺，上街抗議，「暴徒」推倒裝甲車，無懼水炮與催淚彈夾擊，餐廳恕不招待軍裝，連串反攻防暴警的畫面，是翻牆版自由之夏！茂名官幹見勢頭不對，四日之後宣告火葬場「壽終正寢」！茂名政府點解唔暫緩呢？林奠由強推送中條例到暫緩，拖了四個月。自稱阿bill已經dead再用一個月。正式落刀切，又多等兩個月。香港被林奠蹂躪大半年，年輕人被墮樓被浮屍被射頭被爆眼被輪姦，全港市民食了過萬支TG，近六千人遭濫捕。民意，一天內以海嘯般的160萬+選票將建制區議員滅頂！亡黨！茂名黨幹，決定不做林奠茂名翻版，與香港特衰政權切得乾乾淨淨過太監！人文生態園項目，化作一縷灰煙，遙向特區寶福山飄送。<br />\n<br />\n這大半年香港確實遭逢人文生態大災難，人權與人道在警暴中淪喪。重複689語言偽術，偷天換日以檢討代替獨立調查的林奠，成功將工聯會民建聯變為condom，後者據傳要搵商界大水喉射住一班落選議員，四年薪津累計要1.6億。擔心唔知幾時被砌曱甴王的地產闊佬，今時今日還會疏爽獻金？抑或加大力度送這班契弟入「人文生態園」永不超生，着數些？ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f1a019bf1acef0e06848848dc99ff89f6eace1a3","tid":1768925,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05f28b4da7a36e077bd7bbbe64bf9e004ed686cc","tid":1768925,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"有無人知一個月前嘅今日係咩日子？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ddceecaa2698e2a935ba5e99d53a53fb0a408b7b","tid":1768925,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}